    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>Share your story</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A short questionnaire or a conversation — however you'd rather tell it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>We listen carefully</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We read between the lines for the details that actually matter to you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>We thoughtfully write</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">A first draft, written to sound like you on your most articulate day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal">
        <h4>You review</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">Read it aloud. Sit with it. Tell us what feels off, if anything does.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h4>Together we refine</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">We adjust tone, trim length, and sharpen the moments that matter most.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h4>You confidently speak</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">The words are ready. So are you. The moment is entirely yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

